        {
            "title": "日韓股市初段個別發展 日股假後復市暫跌逾1% 韓股再破頂",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">日韓股市今早初段個別發展，日股經過昨天假期後今日復市，暫再跌逾1%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/12/20231221_FI_source-ap_日股_東京證交所.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/12/20231221_FI_source-ap_日股_東京證交所.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">截至香港時間上午約8時08分，日經平均指數跌636點或1.06%，報59281點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">南韓首爾綜合指數暫報6746點，升55點或0.82%。</p>\n</div>",
